# Boat O'Craigo Design System

Before making any changes, read:

- `docs/BOAT-O-CRAIGO-DESIGN-SYSTEM.md`
- `docs/BOAT-O-CRAIGO-CURSOR-RULES.md`
- `assets/boc-design-tokens.css`

These files are the design source of truth. Do not introduce a new visual style or component pattern that conflicts with them.

## Critical rules

- Never use `#F0F5ED`
- Do not redesign the approved header or footer
- Do not invent new colours, fonts, gradients, rounded cards, shadows, or animations
- Product card Add to Cart buttons use `#212121`
- Product collection images: white background, no padding, no bottle shadow, no hover movement
- Reuse existing `boc-*` components before creating new sections
- Build page content as merchant-editable Shopify sections and blocks
- Limit the site to the approved ten-template architecture
- Run `shopify theme check` before completion
- Report any design-system deviation before implementing it

## Approved templates

Homepage, Collection, Product, Wine Club, Visit, What's On, About, Book Now, Contact, Customer Account

## CSS tokens

Use variables and classes from `assets/boc-design-tokens.css` (e.g. `--boc-ink`, `.boc-btn--primary`, `.boc-container`, `.boc-product-image`).
